msgid "More visibility modifiers"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/module-system/more-visibility-modifiers.md:3
msgid ""
"![Minimum Rust version: 1.18](https://img.shields.io/badge/"
"Minimum%20Rust%20Version-1.18-brightgreen.svg)"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/module-system/more-visibility-modifiers.md:5
msgid ""
"You can use the `pub` keyword to make something a part of a module's public "
"interface. But in addition, there are some new forms:"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/module-system/more-visibility-modifiers.md:14
msgid ""
"The first form makes the `Foo` struct public to your entire crate, but not "
"externally. The second form is similar, but makes `Bar` public for one other "
"module, `a::b::c` in this case."
msgstr ""
